1.0.name: wordpress/hide-wpengine-tab
1.0.description: WPEngine is a fantastic Wordpress hosting provider with an absolutely fantastic function - the one click staging environment. This plugin is built to make it super easy to limit access to that button so that people don't accidentally overwrite the staging environment.
